description:
Alex Monaco shares his picks for Week 6 of the NFL season starting with Josh Allen and the Bills taking on Patrick Mahomes and the Chiefs, the Cowboys looking to give Jalen Hurts and the Eagles their first loss without Dak Prescott, Justin Jefferson and the Vikings vs Tyreek Hill and the Dolphins, and much more! #Volume #Herd #ColinCowherd
